These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: lavender, green, amber, mauve, yellow, ivory
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, mirinda, iced-tea, tea, sprite
House: art-deco, wooden, modern, townhouse, colonial, futuristic
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, helicopter, roller, taxi
 1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the colonial house is between the wooden house and the person drinking mirinda##2
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the modern house is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 8. the wooden house is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
15. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
16. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Color          | ivory   | lavender     | green | mauve     | amber     | yellow   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | tea  | mirinda  | sprite | cola | fanta |
| House         | wooden | colonial | modern | townhouse    | art-deco  | futuristic |
| Transport     | boat     | helicopter    | bike    | roller   | taxi      | car    |

